data.description: Step into this lovely one owner home, open concept kitchen and living! Four bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms in a split floor plan. 4th bedroom could be an office with easy access to 3rd bathroom. Extra details in the main bedroom include beams on ceiling, large bathroom with tub and walk in shower and large walk in closet! Large kitchen island is wonderful or entertaining. Step into the pristine backyard with large custom patio and firepit, with very well kept grass! Home has solar, available for buyer to assume loan, keeping electric costs relatively low and predictable! Please ask about VA assumable loan with low interest rate!
